data.Name: Nothing In Common
data.Bio: NOTHING IN COMMON was a band from Cologne, Germany. With an amazing mix of influences like LEATHERFACE, JAWBREAKER, SAMIAM, and even some classic rock, they were truly one of the best bands Germany ever produced. Let alone the world! One of the most passionate, real, and honest songwriters so it was quite sad when they decided to call it a day in August 2008 after releasing their best album to date.
